days), or (c) in the case of Universal Credit, paragraph 19A to the Universal Credit Regulations 2013 (waiting days)1 and paragraph 16A to the Universal Credit (Transitional Provisions) Regulations 2014 (waiting days) 2 have been entitled to that allowance. (3) Where the defect referred to in paragraph 7 of Schedule 1 to this scheme (application by telephone)— (a) is corrected within one month (or such longer period as the authority considers reasonable) of the date the authority last drew attention to it, the authority must treat the application as if it had been duly made in the first instance;

